---
<section class="relative min-h-screen flex items-center justify-center py-32 px-6">
  <div class="relative z-10 text-center max-w-4xl mx-auto">
    <span class="inline-block text-emerald-400 text-sm font-semibold tracking-widest uppercase mb-6 border border-emerald-500/30 bg-emerald-500/10 px-4 py-1.5 rounded-full">
      TPQ Solutions
    </span>
    <h1 class="text-5xl md:text-7xl font-bold tracking-tight mb-6 leading-tight">
      Tecnología que<br />entiende <span class="text-emerald-400">tu trabajo.</span>
    </h1>
    <p class="text-lg md:text-xl text-slate-400 mb-10 max-w-2xl mx-auto leading-relaxed">
      Soluciones informáticas para comercios, profesionales y productores rurales.
      Sin vueltas técnicas, solo herramientas que funcionan.
    </p>
    <div class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row gap-4 justify-center">
      <a href="https://wa.me/5492216225776" target="_blank" class="bg-emerald-600 hover:bg-emerald-500 text-white px-8 py-4 rounded-full font-semibold transition-all">
        Escribinos por WhatsApp
      </a>
      <a href="#servicios" class="border border-slate-700 hover:border-slate-500 text-slate-300 px-8 py-4 rounded-full font-semibold transition-all">
